Who likes Cats and MacBook Pros?! This month from May 1st-24th Arm The Animals is doing an amazing giveaway! The prize of the Giveaway will be your choice of either a FREE TRIP for 2 from anywhere in the Continental US to @catconla OR a MacBook Pro. 
The trip will include plane flight, 2 night hotel stay and free admission to @catconla OR a new 15” MacBook Pro! 
Every $20 you spend on the ATA website gets you an entry to win!

As always, for 10% off your order, simply FOLLOW THE LINK in our bio and enter "CATSWITHTHEIRTONGUESOUT" upon checkout!

So which would you choose!? @catconla or MacBook?!
